  'description' => 
  array (
    'en_US' => '<p><img style="margin: 0px 15px 15px 0px; width: 250px; height: auto; float: left;" src="/public/journals/1/journalThumbnail_hr_HR.jpg" alt="Geoadria" />Geoadria is a scientific journal issued by the Croatian Geographic Society in Zadar and Department of Geography at the University of Zadar. It was first issued in 1996 and until 2001 it was published annually. From 2002 it is published biannually. From 2006 all papers in the journal are published in Croatian and English language.</p><p>Status: Active</p><p>ISSN (Print): <a title="ISSN Geoadria" href="http://katalog.nsk.hr/F/STV9A3HDGIKUIFT34Q1BUFXSV42Q82KLG88LFFAFR2P59D823I-02094?func=full-set-set&amp;set_number=051677&amp;set_entry=000002&amp;format=999" target="_blank">1331-2294</a><br />ISSN (Online): <a title="eISSN Geoadria" href="http://katalog.nsk.hr/F/STV9A3HDGIKUIFT34Q1BUFXSV42Q82KLG88LFFAFR2P59D823I-03062?func=full-set-set&amp;set_number=051702&amp;set_entry=000001&amp;format=999" target="_blank">1848-9710</a></p><p>Publisher/s: Croatian Geographical Society - Zadar ; Department of Geography, University of Zadar</p><p>Year of publication of the first issue: 1996</p><p>Frequency: biannual</p><p>Scientific areas: geology; geophysics; demography; geography</p><div><a title="Geoadria RSS" href="/index.php/geoadria/gateway/plugin/WebFeedGatewayPlugin/rss2" target="_blank"> <img style="float: left; display: inline;" src="/public/rss.png" alt="RSS Geoadria" /></a>  <img style="float: left; display: inline;" src="/public/twitter.png" alt="Twitter Geoadria" /> <img style="float: left; display: inline;" src="/public/facebook.png" alt="Facebook Geoadria" /> <img style="float: left; display: inline;" src="/public/email.png" alt="E-mail contact" /></div>',
    'hr_HR' => '<p><img style="margin: 0px 15px 15px 0px; width: 250px; height: auto; float: left;" src="/public/journals/1/journalThumbnail_hr_HR.jpg" alt="Geoadria" />Geoadria je znanstveni časopis kojeg izdaju Hrvatsko geografsko društvo – Zadar i Odjel za geografiju Sveučilišta u Zadru od 1996. Časopis je do 2001. izlazio jednom godišnje, a od 2002. godišnje se objavljuju dva broja. Od 2006. godine svi se članci u časopisu objavljuju na hrvatskom i engleskom jeziku.</p><p>Status: Aktivan</p><p>ISSN (Tisak): 1331-2294<br />ISSN (Online): 1848-9710</p><p>Nakladnik/ici: Hrvatsko geografsko društvo - Zadar ; Odjel za geografiju, Sveučilište u Zadru</p><p>Početak izlaženja: 1996</p><p>Učestalost izlaženja: Polugodišnje</p><p>Znanstveno područje/polje: geologija ; geofizika ; demografija ; geografija</p><div><a title="Geoadria RSS" href="/index.php/geoadria/gateway/plugin/WebFeedGatewayPlugin/rss2" target="_blank"> <img style="float: left; display: inline;" src="/public/rss.png" alt="RSS Geoadria" /></a>  <img style="float: left; display: inline;" src="/public/twitter.png" alt="Twitter Geoadria" /> <img style="float: left; display: inline;" src="/public/facebook.png" alt="Facebook Geoadria" /> <img style="float: left; display: inline;" src="/public/email.png" alt="E-mail contact" /></div>',
